item.title: 【Singles (lossy)】Dolby Atmos - ATB, Topic, A7S - Your Love (9PM) (Dolby Atmos)
item.description:
Note: New Source, had to tinker with the file in order for it to be compatible with iPhone's and other Apple Devices. The Complexity Index being set to "Not Present" makes the file only be read as a Dolby Digital Plus file on iPhone. After tooling around with ffmpeg and MP4Box for several hours, I finally made it compatible, however metadata and tags were lost in the conversion. This will only be a thing on any rips I do that are sourced from Amazon Music, any of my Tidal rips won't be a problem. Enjoy!
